Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,TENHO CHUUREN POUTOU
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.04,0:00:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We win.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.81,0:00:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Be a ringer for me once more
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.81,0:00:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,A chitoitsu.\N(all pairs hand)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.35,0:00:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,He turns down each pair when he's got one?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.69,0:00:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,How did he read my discards?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.52,0:00:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Interesting game you're having there, isn't it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.26,0:00:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't you let me mix it up too?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.66,0:00:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiroyuki,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.55,0:00:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Change with me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.12,0:00:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.12,0:00:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,you can't beat this boomer
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.22,0:00:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,My playing...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.15,0:00:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,won't be a problem, will it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.15,0:00:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,N-no
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.15,0:00:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm thankful with all my heart for what you're doing, Ten
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.65,0:00:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this changing shit?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.75,0:00:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.25,0:00:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I ain't afraid\N(Kansai dialect)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.85,0:00:57.21,Default - white - top,,0,0,0,,2nd Game\NEast Hand 1
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.31,0:01:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.71,0:01:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,How does he have such faith that he'll complete his hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.96,0:01:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like he's extremely confident
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.02,0:01:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I start playing and after some hours...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.16,0:01:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I can read the way the tiles are flowing
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.56,0:01:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,My Chitoitsu hands have been called amazing
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.31,0:01:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,This sense of mine
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.31,0:01:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,this is what people have said
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.22,0:02:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron.\NA Chitoitsu
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.28,0:02:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet another Chitoitsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.99,0:02:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,How can he win in this uncanny way?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.51,0:02:26.71,Default - white - top,,0,0,0,,2nd Game\NEast Hand 3
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.91,0:02:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.54,0:02:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I can lay down my triplets as I complete them too
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.45,0:03:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no reason you have to be the only one...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.42,0:03:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,showing your hand's progress
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.59,0:03:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.59,0:03:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't underestimate me
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.48,0:03:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not in Tenpai.\NI'm not either
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.06,0:03:41.28,Default - top - cyan,,0,0,0,,#/tv/shows Hit or miss I guess they never miss huh TikTok|1 HOUR LOOP\Npresents:
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.79,0:03:48.58,default - cyan - with - background,,0,0,0,,カンカン照り ギラついた \N太陽みたいな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.79,0:03:48.58,Default - white - with - background,,0,0,0,,Blazing hot, like the blistering sun
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.28,0:03:46.15,Default - white,,0,0,0,,{\pos(512,476)}Ten Takeshi
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.35,0:03:46.15,Default - red,,0,0,0,,{\pos(258,708)}Kishitani Goro
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.06,0:03:53.24,default - cyan - with - background,,0,0,0,,あいつがまた帰ってきた
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.06,0:03:53.24,Default - white - with - background,,0,0,0,,He's come back again
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.91,0:03:54.71,Default - white,,0,0,0,,{\pos(770,400)}Igawa Hiroyuki
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.91,0:03:54.71,Default - red,,0,0,0,,{\pos(744,630)}Furukawa Yuki
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.29,0:03:59.42,default - cyan - with - background,,0,0,0,,ざわざわと
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.29,0:03:59.42,Default - white - with - background,,0,0,0,,In anxiety...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.95,0:04:05.06,default - cyan - with - background,,0,0,0,,息を殺して
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.95,0:04:05.06,Default - white - with - background,,0,0,0,,you hold your breath
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.58,0:04:03.38,Default - red,,0,0,0,,{\pos(300,710)}Yoshida Eisaku
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.58,0:04:03.38,Default - white,,0,0,0,,{\pos(500,512)}Akagi Shigeru
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.06,0:04:10.44,default - cyan - with - background,,0,0,0,,誰の肩に止まるかな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.06,0:04:10.44,Default - white - with - background,,0,0,0,,Whose shoulder will it land upon
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.44,0:04:16.44,default - cyan - with - background,,0,0,0,,くるくる廻る天道虫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.44,0:04:16.44,Default - white - with - background,,0,0,0,,Ladybug going round and round
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.44,0:04:20.80,default - cyan - with - background,,0,0,0,,背中の星が揃ったら
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.44,0:04:20.80,Default - white - with - background,,0,0,0,,When the stars on her back align
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.80,0:04:30.71,default - cyan - with - background,,0,0,0,,雨上がりの風吹く通りを
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.80,0:04:30.71,Default - white - with - background,,0,0,0,,After the rain, above the windswept street,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.78,0:04:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,#/tv/shows subs: "They're better than nothing!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.71,0:04:32.98,default - cyan - with - background,,0,0,0,,陽が昇った
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.71,0:04:32.98,Default - white - with - background,,0,0,0,,The sun rose
