Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.59,0:04:37.92,Default - white,,0,0,0,,{\pos(642,594)}Episode 3
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.59,0:04:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(632,444)}Ten: Tenho-doori no Kaidanji\N(The Nice Guy on Tenho Way)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.58,0:04:42.41,Default - white - top,,0,0,0,,2nd Game\NEast Hand 4
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.56,0:04:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Again
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.62,0:04:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten is trying to provoke Murota and destroy his pace, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.56,0:04:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,this style of playing, it's Murota's specialty
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.54,0:04:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten is entering his opponent's home turf,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.31,0:04:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,and explicitly asking for a contest
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.25,0:05:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,He's already in Tenpai.\NAs I thought, he's like a monster
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.14,0:05:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What tile is he waiting on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.14,0:05:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The dora is Red Dragon
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.99,0:05:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,He's probably holding low Sou tiles?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.14,0:05:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how you put it, this is...(dangerous)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.28,0:05:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It passed!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.82,0:06:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,This passed too!?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.69,0:06:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You've guessed it haven't you, Hiroyuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.28,0:06:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,A facade
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.65,0:06:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed. A facade
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.59,0:06:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,This character's Mahjong...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.59,0:06:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,is the Mahjong of "giving up"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.55,0:06:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The weapon he uses in making players give up is merely his image
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.39,0:06:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Making himself out to be a monster or a god...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.89,0:06:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,to make players fold, he applies pressure
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.96,0:06:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,but still only progresses at his own pace
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.68,0:06:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But when I did the same thing
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.08,0:06:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,his own pace started to freeze
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.42,0:06:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I dare say
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.15,0:06:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Those pairs you've laid down...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.91,0:06:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,They're make believe.\NThey aren't all pairs at all
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.16,0:07:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You're reckless
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.32,0:07:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.54,0:07:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,TanYao, SanSyoku\N(Only tiles 2-9, from 3 suits)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.28,0:07:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,7,700 points
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.09,0:07:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-you..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.09,0:07:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You ought not have been in Tenpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.65,0:07:48.33,default - cyan,,0,0,0,,You think I'm so fucking dumb I'd tell you the composition of my hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.35,0:07:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been playing in such a profoundly dishonest way...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.22,0:07:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,you shouldn't be trusting anyone, should you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.49,0:08:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,So, let's continue, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.18,0:08:09.48,Default - white - top,,0,0,0,,2nd Game\NSouth Hand 4
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.39,0:08:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,He's got it
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.85,0:08:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,He's in Tenpai
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.76,0:08:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Kan
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.74,0:08:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,At this point he's discarded a 1 and 2 Pin
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.45,0:08:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,He was aiming for a SanSyoku or Tanyao\N(3 Suits, or only tiles 2-8)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.02,0:08:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But he gave up on them...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.02,0:08:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That is to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.02,0:09:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy's got an extra 4 Pin
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.91,0:09:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That end tile there is the extra 4 Pin
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.19,0:09:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten followed it with his eye
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.05,0:09:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Humph.\NHe just now deliberately followed that tile with his eye
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.62,0:09:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Does he think that'll make me feel safe and discard MY 4 Pin or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.96,0:09:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,A PERFECT draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.65,0:09:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But he can't discard his 4 Pin
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.59,0:09:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten to one, Murota is waiting on it
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.76,0:09:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,T-ten! That's the tile Murota's waiting for!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.65,0:10:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,He dealt into Murota's hand
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.62,0:10:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That tile is a 4 Pin!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.14,0:10:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,How?\NI could have sworn...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.48,0:10:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,He ought to have drawn the 4 Pin
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.45,0:10:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,H-how?\NCertainly, just now...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.79,0:10:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The jerk dew that very tile!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.15,0:10:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,How was that tile not a 4 Pin?!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.62,0:10:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,This Dora tile will be tough to discard
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.02,0:10:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I break up a pair?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.02,0:10:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's like confessing I'm not on a single wait
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.68,0:10:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,How about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.16,0:11:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.\NThat 8 Sou I thought was a 4 Pin
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.71,0:11:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,H-he ought not be waiting on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.62,0:11:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,At last... you look up
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.34,0:11:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,TanYao with one Dora.\N3,900 points
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.74,0:11:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.54,0:11:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You've done it Ten
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.12,0:11:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten DID pick up his 4 Pin
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.79,0:11:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But in that instant he switched it for the 8 Sou he just drew
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.62,0:11:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't a cheat
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.62,0:11:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It was all within his own hand
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.62,0:12:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,As I thought. His Mahjong is strong
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.02,0:12:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's as far as it goes
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.08,0:12:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You probably won't be winning any more
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.28,0:12:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You yourself have... "given up"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.96,0:12:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You retreated from a difficult position...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.68,0:12:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and you couldn't read your OWN mind
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.05,0:12:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true all the world round...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.56,0:12:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who crumble under pressure
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.05,0:12:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,have no path to victory
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.19,0:12:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.22,0:12:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't you show this guy out?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.14,0:12:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I already said
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.54,0:12:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm retired
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.54,0:13:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The chairman is constrained for time
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.54,0:13:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you somehow...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.25,0:13:02.76,default - cyan,,0,0,0,,No way
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.76,0:13:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have the stamina for long matches any more
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.65,0:13:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Murota just lost.\NThere's no one else but you
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.42,0:13:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Murota
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.08,0:13:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of guy beat him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.55,0:13:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Some guy named Ten
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.02,0:13:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.54,0:13:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like they'll change a player for the next East South game
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.79,0:13:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I see
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.49,0:13:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.79,0:13:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten, even though you were my opponent,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.56,0:13:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,why did you help me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.28,0:13:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I'd teach you something in front of "Hama-chan"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.92,0:13:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,something about ringers and the REAL world of Mahjong
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.05,0:14:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Time to start again
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.19,0:14:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,AKAGI SHIGERU
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.15,0:14:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Why HIM?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.15,0:14:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Is his Mahjong Strong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.65,0:14:17.91,default - cyan,,0,0,0,,"Strong" isn't a sufficient word for what he is
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.39,0:14:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,During his career no one has been able to defeat him
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.96,0:14:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Without doubt...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.88,0:14:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,a man with the innate ability to blow others away
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.91,0:14:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Until this day he hasn't lost a single game
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.07,0:14:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,A PEERLESS Mahjong professional
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.22,0:14:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Mahjong professional
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.05,0:14:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you Ten?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.75,0:14:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-you know of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.79,0:14:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Rumors... on the wind
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.42,0:14:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Haven't you retired?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.08,0:14:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard about a strong player
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.68,0:14:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a long time
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.68,0:14:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,but I thought I'd try to play him
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.81,0:15:11.11,Default - white - top,,0,0,0,,3rd Game\NEast Hand 1
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.56,0:15:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Akagi Shigeru
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.79,0:15:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,How on earth will he play?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.45,0:15:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Pon
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.82,0:15:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Chii
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.82,0:15:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing.\NIt's only just started,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.91,0:15:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,but already the game's coming to a boil
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.74,0:15:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Simply put, it's not just his speed,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.82,0:16:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The man himself exudes a strange atmosphere
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.02,0:16:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's indescribable, like something in the air
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.68,0:16:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Brilliance
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.68,0:16:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,A brilliance that suggests a further vast capacity for brilliance
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.56,0:16:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This man is overflowing with the strange and unknown
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.65,0:16:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.45,0:16:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Chanta with Red Dragon
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.39,0:16:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Chanta...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.39,0:16:34.59,Default - top - cyan,,0,0,0,,Chanta: All triples and pairs must contain a terminal tile [1 or 9] or honor[dragon or wind]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.39,0:16:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and finished on only the 4th turn?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.51,0:16:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't get my hand moving in only 4 turns
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.56,0:16:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.56,0:16:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You three guys have discarded 9 tiles
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.79,0:16:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I drew 2 of those
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.79,0:16:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,All told, It felt like I drew eleven times
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.51,0:16:57.58,Default - white - top,,0,0,0,,3rd Game\NEast Hand 3
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.16,0:17:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Pon
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.62,0:17:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsumo
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.82,0:17:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Another Chanta?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.95,0:17:38.68,Default - white - top,,0,0,0,,3rd Game\NEast Hand 4
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.42,0:18:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not in Tenpai
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.29,0:18:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenpai
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.29,0:18:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Not his typical consecutive wins...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.56,0:18:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,but once again he was going for a Chanta hand
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.62,0:18:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it about time you play in a more normal style?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.82,0:18:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,No. This will be fine
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.82,0:18:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm still measuring him
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.82,0:18:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Measuring?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.22,0:18:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The Mahjong I'm playing now does not depend upon luck
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.25,0:18:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,In a 100 games...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.25,0:18:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,it'll win 100
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.22,0:18:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Without knowing the general strength of your opponent
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.94,0:18:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,jumping in head first wouldn't do
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.05,0:18:48.25,Default - white - top,,0,0,0,,3rd Game\NSouth Hand 2
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.42,0:19:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Riichi
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.71,0:19:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.85,0:19:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not Chanta
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.94,0:19:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I thought i'd swtich it up some
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.18,0:19:37.71,Default - white - top,,0,0,0,,3rd Game\NSouth Hand 3
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.69,0:19:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Welp, sorry. I haven't got any honor tiles
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.62,0:19:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Riichi
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.94,0:20:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,A... code?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.99,0:20:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.56,0:20:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,If no one noticed I wouldn't know what I'd do
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.14,0:20:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be sad playing with three worthless players
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.45,0:20:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Code?!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.45,0:20:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What's he talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.45,0:20:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiroyuki, you understand by now, don't you
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.99,0:20:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Up to now Akagi's hands have been largely Chanta, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.39,0:20:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He told us which in his discards
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.42,0:20:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The orientation of discarded honor tiles
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.42,0:20:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Upside down means Chanta
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.42,0:20:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsumo
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.39,0:20:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Riichi
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.16,0:20:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Right side up means it's not Chanta
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.11,0:20:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then. This time it's Chanta
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.55,0:21:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you an idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.65,0:21:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.68,0:21:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.91,0:21:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut the fuck up, bitch
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.91,0:21:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just embarrassing yourself by talking
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.54,0:21:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, Ten...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.54,0:21:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,he stopped himself before declaring Riichi
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.59,0:21:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,B-but you turned the character tile!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.36,0:21:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That depends on the situation
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.36,0:21:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Before, when Akagi discarded the 9 Man
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.76,0:21:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have any honor tiles
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.42,0:21:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,If you think of the 9 Man as an honor tile, it was upside down, meaning Chanta
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.16,0:21:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But, strictly speaking, 9 Man is not an honor tile
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.05,0:21:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So therefore you could think it won't be chanta as well
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.16,0:21:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You can see that at first glance...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.94,0:21:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,but you'll understand when you look at Akagi's open hand
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.36,0:21:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If he won with a 1 Sou he'd have Chanta
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.42,0:21:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,with a 4 Sou and it wouldn't be Chanta
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.82,0:22:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That is to say he was waiting on BOTH outcomes and discarded accordingly
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.34,0:22:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That kid watching from the sidelines understands
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.76,0:22:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You've therefore been playing with trash, haven't you Ten?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.75,0:22:21.05,Default - white - top,,0,0,0,,3rd Game\NSouth Hand 4
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.25,0:22:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a bit hungry
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.56,0:22:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you get me something good?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.09,0:22:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Is sushi okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.74,0:22:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Sushi, hunh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.52,0:22:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys...\NThe most delicious thing in the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.88,0:22:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.45,0:22:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Normal people probably say it's fugu or sushi
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.91,0:22:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It ain't that
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.89,0:22:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,For example, when you play Mahjong
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.88,0:22:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,There are those who will bet their entire fortune...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.99,0:23:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,betting on one big play like they're omnipotent...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.25,0:23:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,playing with tiles cut from their very souls
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.22,0:23:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,A tile with a soul riding on it
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.25,0:23:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,When you call "Ron" on such a tile...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.05,0:23:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels like you're devouring their heart... their soul
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.45,0:23:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Compared to that flavor...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.45,0:23:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,fugu or sushi are as good as garbage
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.65,0:23:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,In this world...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.65,0:23:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,people's souls are the most delicious thing of all
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.22,0:23:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Riichi
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.79,0:23:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.76,0:23:53.42,Default - top,,0,0,0,,Baiman\N(24,000 points direct hit)
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.11,0:24:02.91,Default - top,,0,0,0,,We're in a tough spot
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.91,0:24:06.42,Default - top,,0,0,0,,It can be perfectly summed up:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.42,0:24:09.28,Default - top,,0,0,0,,We're going to lose like this
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.28,0:24:14.14,Default - top,,0,0,0,,No.\NAkagi just now...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.14,0:24:16.45,Default - top,,0,0,0,,I could see an opening once or twice
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.45,0:24:20.91,Default - top,,0,0,0,,He progresses with a near perfect game...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.91,0:24:22.91,Default - top,,0,0,0,,HOWEVER
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.91,0:24:28.14,Default - top,,0,0,0,,Deep inside he's thinking this is a load of shit
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.14,0:24:30.65,Default - top,,0,0,0,,Shit
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.65,0:24:36.59,Default - top,,0,0,0,,What he wants most of all isn't winning by staring off into space
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.59,0:24:40.65,Default - top,,0,0,0,,Akagi's heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.65,0:24:42.94,Default - top,,0,0,0,,is he wants a real fight
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.94,0:24:48.05,Default - top,,0,0,0,,He want's to go "all or nothing" more than anyone else.\NThis is Akagi's true nature
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.05,0:24:55.28,Default - top,,0,0,0,,That is the ONLY chink through which I can stab the bastard
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.28,0:24:58.76,Default - top,,0,0,0,,I'll aim there
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.38,0:25:09.11,Default - white - top,,0,0,0,,Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.31,0:25:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The opposite of 100% is 0%.\NYour uncanny luck will be MINE
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.19,0:25:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What we're playing for isn't points...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.45,0:25:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's PRIDE
